{
  "id": "greeting-newyear",
  "name": "新年贺卡",
  "category": "greeting",
  "description": "一张喜庆的新年贺卡，带有灯笼、烟花和金色装饰元素",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "date",
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "date_range",
        "start": "01-01",
        "end": "01-15",
        "description": "元旦至元宵节期间触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "lunar_newyear",
        "description": "农历新年期间触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "year": {
      "type": "year",
      "description": "年份"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "收卡人名称"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "送卡人名称"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "新年祝福内容"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一段新年祝福语。\n\n背景信息：\n- 送卡人：{{sender}}\n- 收卡人：{{recipient}}\n- 年份：{{year}}\n- 关系：{{relationship}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容喜庆吉祥，充满新年氛围\n2. 语气要符合送卡人的性格特点\n3. 可以包含对新一年的美好祝愿\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n5. 要有传统节日感\n\n请直接输出祝福内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "festive",
    "colors": ["#ffd700", "#ff6b35", "#1a1a2e"],
    "mood": "喜庆祥和"
  },
  "rarity": "seasonal",
  "collectible": true
}